and maybe possibly a violation of someone

00:56:03.819 --> 00:56:11.559
else's privacy and their rights to go about
their life without, you know, being posted

00:56:11.559 --> 00:56:15.709
online. So, again, you have to weigh the good
and the bad and you have to decide for yourself.

00:56:15.709 --> 00:56:20.170
Every one has to decide for themselves how
they want to view this. And there's been a

00:56:20.170 --> 00:56:24.980
lot of talk about this, the rise of the transparent
society where everything is on camera so every

00:56:24.980 --> 00:56:32.400
one is equal. But, I'm not sure that it's
really working out that way so far. Okay,

00:56:32.400 --> 00:56:36.589
thanks very much.

